    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="网页相关概念"><a href="#网页相关概念" class="headerlink" title="网页相关概念"></a>网页相关概念</h3><ul><li>服务器: 是用来存储客户数据i并提供随时数据查询功能的计算机,一般需要24小时稳定工作,否则会造成用户访问失败</li><li>浏览器: 用户在PC端/MAC端/移动设备等安装的用于访问网络页面数据的软件,常用的浏览器有以下:<ul><li>微软公司——-IE————–对应内核Trident </li><li>谷歌公司——-Chrome—–对应内核Blink</li><li>苹果公司——-Safari——–对应内核Webkit</li><li>欧朋公司——-Opera——- 对应内核Blink</li><li>Mozilla——— Firefox——对应内核Gecko</li></ul></li><li>网页: 用户通过浏览器在地址栏上 输入对应网址或点击超链接后获得的页面称为网页,具体的活动过程如下<ul><li>请求: 用户通过浏览器像服务器发起http协议文字/图片/音频/视频等数据请求</li><li>响应: 服务器收到后再通过http协议返回给浏览器,浏览器通过内核引擎渲染出相应的页面<img src="https://gitee.com/Kyle1106/myBlogImgs/raw/master/img/20200312215049.png" alt=""></li></ul></li></ul><h3 id="HTML相关概念"><a href="#HTML相关概念" class="headerlink" title="HTML相关概念"></a>HTML相关概念</h3><ul><li>HTML: Hyper Text Markup Language，超文本标记语言,之所以称为超文本是因为页面内可以包含图片甚至音视频等数据,其中的标记,我们更习惯称为标签或者元素,如下图所示,一个html页面包含多个标签内容<img src="https://gitee.com/Kyle1106/myBlogImgs/raw/master/img/20200312215721.png" alt=""></li><li>标签关系分类<ul><li>嵌套关系(父子关系)</li><li>并列关系(兄弟关系)</li></ul></li><li>标签分类<ul><li>单标签: 少数如br/input等不需要包裹内容的功能性标签</li><li>双标签: 大部分标签都是双标签,如p/h1~h6/div等</li></ul></li><li>标签属性: 为标签增加功能并使用特定字符的内容,属性有以下特点<ul><li>标签可以同时有多个属性，并且属性之间以空格隔开（可读性、规范）</li><li>标签名与属性名之间，必须以空格隔开</li><li>属性与属性之间没有顺序关系</li><li>每个标签上的属性并不是完全相同</li><li>标签通用属性:class/id/title等</li></ul></li><li>HTML完整骨架</li></ul><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- 告诉浏览器当前页面是HTML5页面，让浏览器用HTML5的标准去解析识别HTML文档 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- 必须放在HTML文档的最前面，不能省略，省略了会出现兼容性问题 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- HTML文档的根元素，一个文档中只能有一个,其他元素皆为后代 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;!DOCTYPE <span class="meta-keyword">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- lang属性为W3C推荐使用属性,作用是告诉浏览器网页展示所用语言 进而利用浏览器的翻译和语音合成工具 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">html</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">"en"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 告诉浏览器用哪种编码解析html文件 如果不设置默认为UTF-8 注意解码和编码字符集不一样会导致页面乱码 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">charset</span>=<span class="string">"UTF-8"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 设置页面标题 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span>标题<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 页面内容部分 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    页面内容</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>图片/音频/视频/文本文件等资源导入方式<ul><li>采用绝对路径: <ul><li>本地资源(不推荐使用)<ul><li><code>src=&quot;file:///C:/Users/Kyle/Desktop/dog.jpg&quot;</code></li><li><code>src=&quot;C:\Users\Kyle\Desktop\dog.jpg&quot;</code></li></ul></li><li>远程资源<ul><li><code>src=&quot;https://github.com/Kyles1106/img/dog.jpg&quot;</code></li></ul></li></ul></li><li>采用相对路径:<ul><li>同级目录(./可以省略)<ul><li><code>src=&quot;./dog.jpg&quot;</code></li></ul></li><li>上级目录<ul><li><code>src=&quot;../dog.jpg&quot;</code></li></ul></li><li>下级目录(images跟当前html同目录的文件夹 里面带有dog.jpg)<ul><li><code>src=&quot;images.dog.jpg&quot;</code></li></ul></li></ul></li></ul></li><li>常见标签及属性一览</li></ul><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br><span class="line">70</span><br><span class="line">71</span><br><span class="line">72</span><br><span class="line">73</span><br><span class="line">74</span><br><span class="line">75</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;!DOCTYPE <span class="meta-keyword">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">html</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">"en"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">charset</span>=<span class="string">"UTF-8"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">"viewport"</span> <span class="attr">content</span>=<span class="string">"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span>Document<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">&lt;!-- h系列(Header)标题标签 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 作用:  给页面上的文字加上标题的语义 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 特点:  文字加粗 大小随着级别越大而变小 每个标题独占一行  并且有上下边距--&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 注意:  在一个页面中,h1只能给logo或者网站标题使用 滥用不利于SEO(搜索引擎优化) --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h1</span>&gt;</span>我是h1标签<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h1</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h2</span>&gt;</span>我是h2标签<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h2</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h3</span>&gt;</span>我是h3标签<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h3</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h4</span>&gt;</span>我是h4标签<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h4</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h5</span>&gt;</span>我是h5标签<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h5</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h6</span>&gt;</span>我是h6标签<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h6</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">&lt;!-- p(Paragraph)段落标签 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 作用:  给页面上的一段文字加上段落的语义 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 特点:  每个段落独占一行 并且有上下边距--&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span>我是段落内容我是段落内容我是段落内容<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">&lt;!-- hr(Horizontal Rule)水平线标签 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 作用:  在页面上显示一条水平横线,起到分隔效果,实际开发中不常用  --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 注意:  hr为单标签 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">hr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">&lt;!-- br(Break Row)换行标签 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 作用:  用来强制换行 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 注意:  br为单标签 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">br</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 以下是四组文本格式化标签 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 第1组 没有语义的弃用标签 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">b</span>&gt;</span>我是带有加粗效果的b标签<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">b</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">u</span>&gt;</span>我是带有下划线效果的u标签<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">u</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">i</span>&gt;</span>我是带有倾斜效果的i标签<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">i</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">s</span>&gt;</span>我是带有删除线效果的s标签<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">s</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 第2组 带有语义的推荐标签 用以加强语气 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">strong</span>&gt;</span>我是带有加粗效果的strong标签<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">strong</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ins</span>&gt;</span>我是带有下划线效果的ins标签<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ins</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">em</span>&gt;</span>我是带有倾斜效果的em标签<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">em</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">del</span>&gt;</span>我是带有删除线效果的del标签<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">del</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">&lt;!-- img(Image)图片标签 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 作用:  在页面中显示一张图片 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 属性: </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">    src:  表示图片位置</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">    alt:  表示图片加载失败时的提示文字</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">    title:表示鼠标移入图片时显示的文字</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">    width/height:设置图片宽高 单位为px 可以省略当设置其中一个时图片会按照原比例缩放,因此为了防止变形 一般只设置其中一个</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">   --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">img</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"images/dog.jpg"</span> <span class="attr">alt</span>=<span class="string">"这是一张狗狗图片"</span> <span class="attr">title</span>=<span class="string">"可爱吧?"</span> <span class="attr">width</span>=<span class="string">"300"</span> <span class="attr">height</span>=<span class="string">"300"</span>&gt;</span> </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">&lt;!-- a(Anchor)超链接标签 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 作用:  在页面中显示一个带下划线的蓝色链接,用来跳转页面或者下载文件 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 注意:  链接点击前为蓝色,点击后为深褐色,刷新浏览器缓存后可变灰蓝色 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 属性:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">    href: 表示跳转的页面或者文件路径</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">    target: 用来表示跳转方式</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">    _self:  默认值,表示在原标签页中打开</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">    _blank: 表示在标签页中打开</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">  --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">a</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">"https://github.com/Kyles1106"</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">a</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
